                  <description>Instead of making a 近战 Attack, a model with a weapon with this special rule may make a special attack at Initiative step 2. This automatically
                                        inflicts a single Hit against each model (friendly or enemy) in contact with the attacking model’s base, using the profile of the weapon with this special rule.
