        <rule id="f3ee-60e7-e8ed-bf54" name="Prehensile Dataspike" publicationId="bde1-6db1-163b-3b76" page="123" hidden="false">
          <description>A model equipped with a prehensile dataspike may make an additional single attack per turn as well as any they would normally be eligible to make. These attacks are
                        made using the weapon profiles shown below.
